  "short_description": "Gather your fearless allies in the heart-pounding realms of Fiesta Online, where the fate of Isya rests on your shoulders. Prepare to wage war against the malevolent grip of Legel's corruption, forging powerful bonds with fellow adventurers as you embark on quests that will push you to your limits.",
